data.description: This is a classic two story beauty in Pecan Ridge! Recently built home with attention to detail. Lots of space, huge rooms, neutral colors throughout. Formal living room and dining room, large den with extra living space. The very spacious kitchen has a work island, tons of cabinets and granite counterspace that is sure to please any chef. The primary suite has a deep closet and all bathrooms have a dual vanity.
